1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
ظآزIt's a sordid story that you've madeظآز

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
ظآزUp to fill my mind with doubts and painظآز

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
ظآزBlood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?ظآز

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
ظآزEnjoying what's mineظآز

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
ظآزHave you found a way
to bury guilt and shameظآز

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
ظآزI'm coming back to lifeظآز

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
ظآزThrough the seven gates of deathظآز

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
ظآزI'm coming back survivedظآز

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
ظآزFeeling great to see you fallظآز

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
ظآزI'm taking back what's mineظآز

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
ظآزBringing horror to the battlefieldظآز

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
ظآزLay it to wasteظآز

13
