ظآزTil the day my kingdom is reclaimedظآز

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,037 --> 00:01:46,000
=Episode 3=

16
00:01:47,437 --> 00:01:48,198
This is

17
00:01:48,198 --> 00:01:49,758
the letter to all shareholders

18
00:01:50,478 --> 00:01:51,790
that was never officially issued.

19
00:01:52,838 --> 00:01:55,758
I hope that at the shareholders'
meeting three days from now,

20
00:01:56,517 --> 00:01:57,758
you will support

21
00:01:58,437 --> 00:01:59,397
my reappointment.

22
00:02:05,118 --> 00:02:07,597
But this isn't something

23
00:02:07,597 --> 00:02:08,677
I can decide alone.

24
00:02:22,677 --> 00:02:23,900
Dongchao, oh Dongchao.

25
00:02:24,397 --> 00:02:26,557
You really are as visionary as ever.

26
00:02:26,997 --> 00:02:28,598
You never fight unprepared.

27
00:02:29,078 --> 00:02:30,078
Before coming here,

28
00:02:30,078 --> 00:02:31,277
you had convinced my brother

29
00:02:31,277 --> 00:02:32,677
and all the shareholders.

30
00:02:38,078 --> 00:02:38,878
Actually, Mr. Li,

31
00:02:39,397 --> 00:02:40,397
I know you've recently

32
00:02:40,397 --> 00:02:42,277
reconciled with your family.

33
00:02:42,797 --> 00:02:43,438
I don't want

34
00:02:43,438 --> 00:02:44,837
this small matter of mine

35
00:02:45,110 --> 00:02:46,837
to become the reason
you and your brothers

36
00:02:47,117 --> 00:02:48,397
fall out again.

37
00:02:48,717 --> 00:02:49,517
So,

38
00:02:49,758 --> 00:02:51,318
I spoke with them myself.

39
00:02:53,117 --> 00:02:55,198
I appreciate their trust in me.

40
00:02:55,717 --> 00:02:56,638
They are supporting

41
00:02:56,638 --> 00:02:57,878
my reappointment.

42
00:02:59,717 --> 00:03:00,517
Mr. Li,

43
00:03:02,837 --> 00:03:04,358
we have never been enemies.

44
00:03:06,038 --> 00:03:06,837
I'm

45
00:03:09,478 --> 00:03:11,158
your most loyal ally

46
00:03:12,438 --> 00:03:13,438
and your brother.

47
00:03:18,397 --> 00:03:19,198
Then,

48
00:03:20,117 --> 00:03:21,318
I'll take my leave.

49
00:03:36,918 --> 00:03:37,638
Tina.

50
00:03:37,758 --> 00:03:38,557
The medicine.

51
00:03:39,478 --> 00:03:40,277
Ms. Bai.

52
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:51,038
Take this medicine
and remember the name.

53
00:03:51,598 --> 00:03:52,717
Tell Mr. Jiang you took

54
00:03:52,717 --> 00:03:55,038
the wrong pills due to stress,
which led to this mistake.

55
00:03:58,598 --> 00:03:59,638
You want me

56
00:03:59,638 --> 00:04:01,078
to be like Rao Yuci,

57
00:04:02,717 --> 00:04:03,677
so everyone thinks

58
00:04:03,677 --> 00:04:05,078
I've gone crazy?

59
00:04:05,837 --> 00:04:06,638
Ms. Bai.

60
00:04:06,677 --> 00:04:07,638
Mr. Jiang on line A.

61
00:04:08,397 --> 00:04:09,198
Put him through.

62
00:04:09,198 --> 00:04:09,837
Okay.

63
00:04:14,198 --> 00:04:15,397
Hello, Mr. Jiang.

64
00:04:16,157 --> 00:04:16,957
Do people at Lysen

65
00:04:16,957 --> 00:04:18,438
line up to jump off the building?

66
00:04:20,717 --> 00:04:21,957
Sorry, Mr. Jiang.

67
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:23,957
Mingxuan's been under
a lot of pressure.

68
00:04:23,957 --> 00:04:24,678
Are you

69
00:04:24,878 --> 00:04:25,717
apologizing

70
00:04:25,717 --> 00:04:26,917
on his behalf or yours?

71
00:04:27,357 --> 00:04:28,638
I'm calling about two things.

72
00:04:28,798 --> 00:04:29,597
First,

73
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:31,477
you will fully cooperate with Rao Yuci

74
00:04:31,477 --> 00:04:32,837
on the Dada Wine Industry project.

75
00:04:33,477 --> 00:04:34,238
But, Mr. Jiang...

76
00:04:34,238 --> 00:04:35,517
I don't want to hear any "but."

77
00:04:38,638 --> 00:04:39,438
Yes.

78
00:04:39,758 --> 00:04:40,597
The second thing.

79
00:04:40,957 --> 00:04:42,198
The person in your room.

80
00:04:43,078 --> 00:04:44,878
I want him out of Lysen

81
00:04:45,238 --> 00:04:46,357
this instant.

82
00:04:46,810 --> 00:04:47,998
I don't want to see him again.

83
00:04:53,238 --> 00:04:54,798
What did Rao Yuci say at the end?

84
00:04:58,277 --> 00:04:59,078
Liangliang.

85
00:05:01,798 --> 00:05:02,878
Have you ever thought

86
00:05:04,597 --> 00:05:06,238
that when we sold Chuxia,

87
00:05:07,118 --> 00:05:08,758
maybe we were wrong?

88
00:05:11,198 --> 00:05:12,277
I don't need a coward

89
00:05:12,277 --> 00:05:13,157
to give me advice.

90
00:05:17,477 --> 00:05:19,118
You're afraid too, aren't you?

91
00:05:20,397 --> 00:05:23,157
Rao Yuci isn't the same person
she was three years ago.

92
00:05:25,558 --> 00:05:26,678
The three of us

93
00:05:27,717 --> 00:05:29,717
won't escape her vengeance.

94
00:05:52,675 --> 00:05:55,275
(Dada Wine Industry Project Report)

95
00:06:01,062 --> 00:06:02,250
(Investment Department 1)

96
00:06:02,862 --> 00:06:05,837
(Yuanjian Capital)

97
00:06:08,597 --> 00:06:09,878
Let's meet tomorrow.

98
00:06:36,758 --> 00:06:38,438
No, don't hurt me! Stop!

99
00:06:38,758 --> 00:06:39,758
Why are you following me?

100
00:06:42,517 --> 00:06:43,638
(Chen Mo)
Xinkang Treatment Center.

101
00:06:44,198 --> 00:06:46,357
Psychological Counselor, Chen Mo.

102
00:06:47,998 --> 00:06:48,798
Rao Yuci.

103
00:06:49,318 --> 00:06:50,998
Follow-up visits are part of my job.

104
00:06:51,318 --> 00:06:52,318
Please cooperate.

105
00:06:52,397 --> 00:06:53,957
I'm fine now. I don't need follow-ups.

106
00:06:53,957 --> 00:06:55,078
Just report back.

107
00:06:55,490 --> 00:06:56,477
No, I just don't get it.

108
00:06:56,477 --> 00:06:57,517
Why are you

109
00:06:57,517 --> 00:06:58,678
so hostile toward doctors?

110
00:06:58,717 --> 00:06:59,477
I only knew

111
00:06:59,477 --> 00:07:00,477
the female doctor,

112
00:07:00,477 --> 00:07:01,438
not you.

113
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,277
The doctor who treats you in the hospital

114
00:07:03,517 --> 00:07:04,998
and the one who does the follow-up

115
00:07:04,998 --> 00:07:06,477
are different doctors.

116
00:07:06,758 --> 00:07:08,878
I'm the one responsible
for the follow-up now.

117
00:07:09,878 --> 00:07:10,438
Let go.

118
00:07:10,438 --> 00:07:11,157
Calm down.

119
00:07:11,957 --> 00:07:12,758
Calm down.

120
00:07:13,318 --> 00:07:14,957
I suggest you cooperate with me.

121
00:07:15,037 --> 00:07:16,238
Whether you've recovered

122
00:07:16,238 --> 00:07:18,238
depends on the periodic report.

123
00:07:18,238 --> 00:07:19,198
If you refuse to cooperate,

124
00:07:19,198 --> 00:07:20,318
- Let go of me.
- I might have to...

125
00:07:33,437 --> 00:07:35,162
(Yuanjian)

126
00:07:43,477 --> 00:07:44,277
What?

127
00:07:44,758 --> 00:07:45,717
You won't even

128
00:07:45,717 --> 00:07:47,238
hide the fact that you're scouting?

129
00:07:48,037 --> 00:07:48,957
I have a meeting

130
00:07:49,078 --> 00:07:49,998
at your office.

131
00:07:50,637 --> 00:07:53,275
(Xian Pengyu of Yuanjian Group)

132
00:07:57,157 --> 00:07:58,917
Someone might take a photo of us.

133
00:07:58,957 --> 00:07:59,837
This is my territory.

134
00:07:59,878 --> 00:08:00,678
Who would dare?

135
00:08:04,758 --> 00:08:06,238
Your boyfriend isn't here anyway.

136
00:08:15,717 --> 00:08:17,357
(Baiying Business Investigation)
Sir, please have a heart.

137
00:08:17,558 --> 00:08:18,357
Any amount will do.

138
00:08:18,357 --> 00:08:18,837
Anything.

139
00:08:18,837 --> 00:08:21,678
Don't bother my customers.
Nothing here. Move along. Go away.

140
00:08:21,678 --> 00:08:22,438
Anything helps.

141
00:08:22,438 --> 00:08:23,238
Just keep moving.

142
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:25,337
(A deaf girl longs to hear.
Illness is cruel, but you can be kind.)

143
00:08:31,318 --> 00:08:32,117
Hello.

144
00:08:32,537 --> 00:08:33,336
Hello.

145
00:08:34,038 --> 00:08:35,558
What service do you need today?

146
00:08:39,078 --> 00:08:41,717
(Zhou Lufeng)
This person, that's you, right?

147
00:08:43,117 --> 00:08:43,918
(Baiying Business, Zhou Lufeng)
That's right.

148
00:08:44,318 --> 00:08:45,117
(Zhou Lufeng of Baiying Business Investigation)
Yes,

149
00:08:45,877 --> 00:08:47,477
I wrote that article a long time ago.

150
00:08:48,117 --> 00:08:49,877
Times have changed since then.

151
00:08:50,038 --> 00:08:51,198
With the market like this,

152
00:08:51,438 --> 00:08:52,518
no one believes it anymore.

153
00:08:53,158 --> 00:08:53,957
I do.

154
00:08:55,558 --> 00:08:57,158
One of your old friends told me

155
00:08:57,158 --> 00:08:58,318
that you're very reliable.

156
00:08:59,597 --> 00:09:00,558
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

157
00:09:00,798 --> 00:09:01,798
I'm Rao Yuci.

158
00:09:07,512 --> 00:09:10,662
(Yu Peidong: Tian Tian, go to
Yuanjian Club and meet Liu Yang.)

159
00:09:10,712 --> 00:09:15,387
(Tian Tian: Yes. I'll go check out
the Dada Wine Industry project.)

160
00:09:16,237 --> 00:09:17,278
Has Liu Yang arrived?

161
00:09:17,318 --> 00:09:18,117
Yes.

162
00:09:19,877 --> 00:09:21,117
Now that's more like it.

163
00:09:21,198 --> 00:09:22,158
Take a look at this.

164
00:09:23,518 --> 00:09:25,158
The one next to him is Huang Xiushui.

165
00:09:25,678 --> 00:09:27,078
Right now, in the baijiu industry,

166
00:09:27,078 --> 00:09:28,398
he's the hottest analyst around.

167
00:09:28,877 --> 00:09:29,717
His following is

168
00:09:29,717 --> 00:09:30,798
huge beyond our imagination.

169
00:09:31,278 --> 00:09:32,318
Even a few foreign funds

170
00:09:32,318 --> 00:09:33,357
take their cues from him.

171
00:09:33,558 --> 00:09:34,918
And his storytelling skills

172
00:09:35,558 --> 00:09:36,717
are top-notch.

173
00:09:41,798 --> 00:09:43,318
That girl is from Lysen Group.

174
00:09:45,078 --> 00:09:45,798
Looks like Lysen

175
00:09:45,798 --> 00:09:47,198
is running out of talent.

176
00:09:47,278 --> 00:09:49,637
You're sending a little white rabbit
into a wolf's den.

177
00:09:49,637 --> 00:09:50,318
Senior.

178
00:09:50,318 --> 00:09:51,038
Thanks.

179
00:09:52,518 --> 00:09:53,798
Did she come alone?

180
00:09:54,438 --> 00:09:55,357
No one else?

181
00:09:56,757 --> 00:09:58,357
Just tell me who you want to ask about.

182
00:09:58,918 --> 00:10:00,038
Give me a name.

183
00:10:02,717 --> 00:10:04,877
This is what we agreed on.

184
00:10:05,117 --> 00:10:06,278
None of this

185
00:10:06,278 --> 00:10:07,078
is a big problem.

186
00:10:08,117 --> 00:10:09,438
Here, drink. Go on.

187
00:10:09,438 --> 00:10:10,237
No.

188
00:10:10,637 --> 00:10:11,438
Drink.

189
00:10:12,312 --> 00:10:13,912
(Baijiu Business Analyst, Huang Xiushui;
Zhaohui Private Equity, Liu Yang.)

190
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,180
Just starting out, little girl?

191
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,558
Which school did you graduate from?

192
00:10:17,078 --> 00:10:18,757
I graduated from Rong Business School.

193
00:10:19,678 --> 00:10:21,877
So you're Liu Yang's junior.

194
00:10:22,637 --> 00:10:23,877
Pleasure to meet you.

195
00:10:26,158 --> 00:10:27,278
Not just any school

196
00:10:27,278 --> 00:10:28,957
can get you into Lysen.

197
00:10:30,398 --> 00:10:31,398
You're too kind.

198
00:10:31,798 --> 00:10:32,837
Very impressive.

199
00:10:33,198 --> 00:10:33,997
Mr. Liu.

200
00:10:36,198 --> 00:10:37,158
Welcome, Ms. Bai.

201
00:10:37,158 --> 00:10:37,957
Ms. Bai.

202
00:10:38,637 --> 00:10:39,438
Mr. Huang.

203
00:10:39,518 --> 00:10:40,558
Let me introduce you.

204
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,250
This is the Vice President
of Lysen Group.

205
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,957
Head of Investment Dept 1.
Bai Liangliang, Ms. Bai.

206
00:10:44,957 --> 00:10:45,678
Hello.

207
00:10:46,518 --> 00:10:47,438
Later on,

208
00:10:47,558 --> 00:10:48,757
I'll tell you all about

209
00:10:48,757 --> 00:10:51,318
your senior's embarrassing stories
at Rong Business School.

210
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,477
Mr. Liu, do you have a moment?

211
00:10:53,477 --> 00:10:54,198
Let's talk.

212
00:10:55,477 --> 00:10:56,198
Sure.

213
00:10:56,198 --> 00:10:56,877
Perfect.

214
00:10:56,877 --> 00:10:57,597
Have a good chat.

215
00:10:57,597 --> 00:10:59,398
I'll chat a bit more with your junior.

216
00:11:00,558 --> 00:11:01,757
Come on, have a seat.

217
00:11:08,398 --> 00:11:09,837
I've been waiting for you.

218
00:11:11,518 --> 00:11:13,078
This is based on my investigation

219
00:11:13,078 --> 00:11:14,117
(Dada Wine Industry)
of the company's supply chain

220
00:11:14,117 --> 00:11:16,158
(Financial Report Investigation)
and analysis of publicly available data.

221
00:11:16,518 --> 00:11:19,158
It reveals the real financial situation
of Dada Wine Industry.

222
00:11:24,798 --> 00:11:25,597
Young lady,

223
00:11:26,678 --> 00:11:27,558
I wish you success.

224
00:11:31,078 --> 00:11:32,558
Why the hurry to meet today?

225
00:11:33,278 --> 00:11:34,757
That's not your style, Ms. Bai.

226
00:11:35,957 --> 00:11:37,357
There can't be

227
00:11:37,357 --> 00:11:38,837
any mistakes with Dada Wine Industry.

228
00:11:39,398 --> 00:11:41,117
Mr. Jiang is distrustful.

229
00:11:41,278 --> 00:11:42,398
You know that well.

230
00:11:43,558 --> 00:11:45,518
We've been planning this for so long.

231
00:11:46,198 --> 00:11:46,997
Besides,

232
00:11:47,398 --> 00:11:48,877
with your help from the inside,

233
00:11:49,198 --> 00:11:50,398
what could go wrong?

234
00:11:58,637 --> 00:11:59,597
Right now,

235
00:11:59,597 --> 00:12:00,918
we're in the same boat.

236
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:01,962
(Power off)

237
00:12:03,477 --> 00:12:04,518
No recording.

238
00:12:05,477 --> 00:12:06,477
Only sincerity.

239
00:12:10,918 --> 00:12:11,717
Ms. Bai,

240
00:12:12,357 --> 00:12:13,757
we're talking business here,

241
00:12:14,398 --> 00:12:15,877
(Power off)
not shooting a spy movie.

242
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,957
Are you sure
Jiang Dongchao will step in?

243
00:12:22,798 --> 00:12:24,757
The channels
to the other directors are open.

244
00:12:24,957 --> 00:12:26,798
With Zhaohui Private Equity
leading the way,

245
00:12:26,798 --> 00:12:28,117
everyone else will enter first.

246
00:12:28,678 --> 00:12:30,877
Then, the wine company
releases perfect financials,

247
00:12:31,117 --> 00:12:32,357
the atmosphere builds,

248
00:12:32,357 --> 00:12:33,357
Jiang Dongchao will

249
00:12:33,357 --> 00:12:34,997
definitely take the bait.

250
00:12:38,957 --> 00:12:39,918
After that,

251
00:12:40,438 --> 00:12:41,877
we just wait for the IPO,

252
00:12:41,877 --> 00:12:44,237
split it up, cash out,
and divide the spoils.

253
00:12:46,637 --> 00:12:47,877
You're mistaken, Mr. Liu.

254
00:12:48,717 --> 00:12:50,318
When Jiang Dongchao publicly announces

255
00:12:50,318 --> 00:12:52,198
that Lysen will participate
in the investment,

256
00:12:52,477 --> 00:12:53,798
my principal and returns

257
00:12:53,798 --> 00:12:54,957
must already be settled

258
00:12:55,117 --> 00:12:55,877
and safely

259
00:12:55,877 --> 00:12:57,158
transferred into my account.

260
00:12:58,597 --> 00:12:59,678
What do you mean, Ms. Bai?

261
00:13:00,597 --> 00:13:01,398
Are you out?

262
00:13:02,117 --> 00:13:03,757
I'm not joking with you.

263
00:13:04,717 --> 00:13:07,278
If Zhaohui could handle
this whole operation alone,

264
00:13:07,477 --> 00:13:09,678
you wouldn't have
asked me to bring Lysen in.

265
00:13:10,278 --> 00:13:11,357
I invested my money early

266
00:13:11,398 --> 00:13:13,717
along with Zhaohui.

267
00:13:14,038 --> 00:13:15,877
That was best display of goodwill.

268
00:13:16,078 --> 00:13:17,278
Our cooperation

269
00:13:17,518 --> 00:13:18,597
ends here.

270
00:13:19,518 --> 00:13:20,637
Lysen comes in,

271
00:13:20,798 --> 00:13:22,278
and I exit safely.

272
00:13:25,398 --> 00:13:26,198
Alright.

273
00:13:26,997 --> 00:13:27,798
Rest assured.

274
00:13:28,438 --> 00:13:29,518
The offstage operations

275
00:13:29,918 --> 00:13:31,117
will be foolproof.

276
00:13:36,010 --> 00:13:38,078
We're still missing one person
to build up the hype.

277
00:13:40,798 --> 00:13:41,918
You mean...

278
00:13:42,637 --> 00:13:44,078
Huang Xiushui.

279
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:48,198
At the presentation,
