Let me tell you...

850
00:37:40,157 --> 00:37:41,518
Young Master Jiang, there you are!

851
00:37:41,518 --> 00:37:42,637
I've been looking for you.

852
00:37:42,958 --> 00:37:44,438
Ms. Bai, where did you run off to?

853
00:37:44,838 --> 00:37:46,237
There are a few investors

854
00:37:46,478 --> 00:37:47,958
I'd like to introduce to you.

855
00:37:47,998 --> 00:37:48,878
Right, right.

856
00:37:48,878 --> 00:37:49,757
Those foreigners?

857
00:37:49,757 --> 00:37:51,237
Tell them to come find me.

858
00:37:51,998 --> 00:37:53,157
Sorry, everyone.

859
00:37:53,330 --> 00:37:54,558
It's a great day for Mr. Jiang.

860
00:37:54,558 --> 00:37:55,717
Come on, enjoy yourselves!

861
00:37:55,717 --> 00:37:56,478
Cheers!

862
00:38:21,317 --> 00:38:22,438
Have the media been notified?

863
00:38:22,677 --> 00:38:23,438
Yes.

864
00:38:23,438 --> 00:38:25,140
It's 4:00 PM today,
at the office entrance.

865
00:38:25,157 --> 00:38:27,078
You'll be in charge of announcing
Lysen's investment

866
00:38:27,237 --> 00:38:28,358
in Dada Wine Industry.

867
00:38:28,518 --> 00:38:30,558
After the announcement,
acquire and dismantle it.

868
00:38:31,677 --> 00:38:33,078
I don't want to see that man

869
00:38:33,078 --> 00:38:34,478
who patted my shoulder ever again.

870
00:38:41,037 --> 00:38:42,800
(Cellar-Aged Spirits)

871
00:38:44,157 --> 00:38:44,958
Tian Tian.

872
00:38:45,558 --> 00:38:46,358
Senior.

873
00:38:48,558 --> 00:38:49,757
Today's launch event

874
00:38:49,757 --> 00:38:50,677
was a huge success.

875
00:38:51,117 --> 00:38:52,518
It's all thanks to you.

876
00:38:52,677 --> 00:38:53,478
Not at all.

877
00:38:53,558 --> 00:38:54,998
I hardly did anything.

878
00:38:55,157 --> 00:38:57,117
Besides, you've already helped me so much.

879
00:38:57,438 --> 00:38:58,918
You even got me into Lysen Group.

880
00:38:59,717 --> 00:39:01,878
I haven't had the chance
to properly thank you yet.

881
00:39:04,237 --> 00:39:05,277
You know, Lysen Group

882
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:06,958
is full of hidden talent.

883
00:39:07,677 --> 00:39:08,958
Establishing yourself here

884
00:39:09,398 --> 00:39:10,717
isn't exactly easy, is it?

885
00:39:12,438 --> 00:39:14,078
There's a great opportunity right now.

886
00:39:14,597 --> 00:39:15,398
What is it?

887
00:39:16,597 --> 00:39:17,438
Mr. Huang.

888
00:39:18,757 --> 00:39:19,558
Think about it.

889
00:39:20,398 --> 00:39:21,117
If you get to know

890
00:39:21,117 --> 00:39:22,157
an expert like him,

891
00:39:22,317 --> 00:39:23,277
it'll be a massive help

892
00:39:23,277 --> 00:39:24,317
with your future work

893
00:39:24,398 --> 00:39:25,797
on this project.

894
00:39:26,398 --> 00:39:27,998
Didn't Ms. Bai mention this to you?

895
00:39:32,757 --> 00:39:33,597
Alright.

896
00:39:33,838 --> 00:39:34,677
I understand.

897
00:39:34,998 --> 00:39:35,797
Good.

898
00:39:36,237 --> 00:39:37,558
Then it's settled.

899
00:39:41,918 --> 00:39:42,878
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

900
00:39:43,237 --> 00:39:45,197
Hello. It's regarding the investors

901
00:39:45,398 --> 00:39:46,717
behind Zhaohui Private Equity

902
00:39:46,717 --> 00:39:48,520
who led the investment
in Dada Wine Industry.

903
00:39:48,838 --> 00:39:49,725
I've found them.

904
00:39:50,317 --> 00:39:52,478
There's one name you'll know very well.

905
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:54,277
I'm coming to see you right now.

906
00:40:23,078 --> 00:40:23,918
Hello, Mr. Huang.

907
00:40:24,438 --> 00:40:25,237
Please, come in.

908
00:40:39,875 --> 00:40:43,520
=Episode 3=
(Hunting Ground)

909
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:46,460
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

910
00:40:46,460 --> 00:40:52,660
ظآزTake a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't sayظآز

911
00:40:53,420 --> 00:40:56,620
ظآزNo need to force your heart anymoreظآز

912
00:40:56,620 --> 00:41:01,140
ظآزSearching for the season
we once missedظآز

913
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:08,660
ظآزLeave this place,
though wounded still stay strongظآز

914
00:41:08,660 --> 00:41:12,580
ظآزYou must believe
one day the rain will fallظآز

915
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:16,620
ظآزAnd wash away the mud
that stains your soulظآز

916
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:20,140
ظآزFind your freedom in the wildظآز

917
00:41:20,140 --> 00:41:24,100
ظآزTake your stride and move aheadظآز

918
00:41:24,100 --> 00:41:28,260
ظآزI will stay behind
and wait for your eyesظآز

919
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:32,460
ظآزTo rebuild
the same flesh and soul againظآز

920
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:36,260
ظآزWander freely through the thornsظآز

921
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:40,340
ظآزKeep walking through the lightظآز

922
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:44,540
ظآزFate is absurd, don't stop for anyoneظآز

923
00:41:44,540 --> 00:41:50,860
ظآزWhat you dare to lose
will one day be your ownظآز

924
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:14,620
ظآزI'm sorry, I still owe you these wordsظآز

925
00:42:14,620 --> 00:42:18,460
ظآزAn apology that came too lateظآز

926
00:42:18,460 --> 00:42:23,100
ظآزYet it's also the path
that saves my soulظآز

927
00:42:23,180 --> 00:42:30,580
ظآزWhen the cold wind
passes it takes the past awayظآز

928
00:42:30,580 --> 00:42:34,660
ظآزYou must believe and stand unwaveringظآز

929
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:38,740
ظآزThere will be hands
to pull you from the deepظآز

930
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:42,740
ظآزFind your freedom in the silenceظآز

931
00:42:42,740 --> 00:42:46,500
ظآزLet your wounds be mendedظآز

932
00:42:46,500 --> 00:42:50,700
ظآزGray is not the past
and pain is not a shameظآز

933
00:42:50,700 --> 00:42:54,860
ظآزSometimes the sunlight
makes the world look cruelerظآز

934
00:42:54,860 --> 00:42:58,580
ظآزWander through the echoes of regretظآز

935
00:42:58,580 --> 00:43:02,620
ظآزBe forgiven and be shelteredظآز

936
00:43:02,620 --> 00:43:06,660
ظآزAfter everything shatters,
hold my handظآز

937
00:43:06,660 --> 00:43:12,860
ظآزA flower reborn
will finally bloom foreverظآز
